@startuml
!include 00-skin.iuml
hide footbox

actor "Uploader" as UP
actor "Admin" as AD
participant "UploadForm" as UF
participant "AdminDashboard" as ADB
participant "UploadController" as UC
participant "AdminController" as AC
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Notification" as NOTIF

== Upload Phase ==
UP -> UF: Fill resource metadata + file
UF -> UC: POST /upload/resource (FormData)
UC -> UC: Validate file type & size
UC -> DB: INSERT INTO resources (is_approved=0)
note right: Resource pending approval
UC --> UF: 201 Resource created
UF -> UP: Show success message

== Approval Phase ==
AD -> ADB: View pending resources
ADB -> AC: GET /admin/resources/pending
AC -> DB: SELECT * WHERE is_approved=0
DB --> AC: list of pending resources
AC --> ADB: Show pending list
AD -> ADB: Click Approve
ADB -> AC: POST /admin/resource/approve/:id
AC -> DB: UPDATE resources SET is_approved=1
AC -> DB: INSERT INTO notifications (uploader_id)
NOTIF --> UP: Resource approved notification
AC --> ADB: 200 Approved
ADB -> AD: Remove from pending list
@enduml
